BIB                  9         17
TITLE      Deuteron-induced reactions on 16O
AUTHOR     (D.Dietzsch,R.A.Douglas,E.F.Pessoa,V.G.Porto,
           E.W.Hamburger,T.Polga,O.Sala,S.M.Perez,P.E.Hodgson)
INSTITUTE  (3BZLUSP,2UK OXF)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,114,330,1968)
           #doi:10.1016/0375-9474(68)90358-8
FACILITY   (VDG,3BZLUSP) The electrostatic accelerator was used.
SAMPLE     A gas target of 99.5% purity was used. The target
           pressure was typically 20 Torr.
METHOD     (TOF)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T,,15.) Estimated error in the absolute
                        cross section
           (ERR-1) Uncertainty in the relative cross section
HISTORY    (20101203C)
           (20251229A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
           The accuracy of data presentation was revised.
           ERR-S -> ERR-1.
ENDBIB              17
COMMON               3          3
EN-ERR     ANG-RSL    ERR-1
